# ── Terraform ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/.terraform/
**/.terraform.lock.hcl

# State files — chứa private keys, passwords, resource IDs
**/terraform.tfstate
**/terraform.tfstate.backup
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.*

# Terraform variable files có thể chứa secrets
**/terraform.tfvars
**/terraform.tfvars.json
**/*.auto.tfvars
**/*.auto.tfvars.json

# Override files
**/override.tf
**/override.tf.json
**/*_override.tf
**/*_override.tf.json

# Plan output (có thể chứa sensitive values)
**/*.tfplan

# ── SSH Keys ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/*.ppk
**/id_rsa
**/id_rsa.pub
**/id_ed25519
**/id_ed25519.pub
**/ec2_key*.pem

# ── Environment & Secrets ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.env
**/secrets.yaml
**/secrets.yml
**/secret.json
**/*credentials*
**/*password*

# ── AWS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/.aws/credentials
**/.aws/config

# ── Node.js ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/node_modules/
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/.npm

# ── OS & IDE ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/.idea/
**/.vscode/
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
